## â“ Why Do We Use Docker?

### ğŸ”¹ Problem Before Docker

Letâ€™s say:
- You build a Python project on your laptop ğŸ’»  
- You send it to your friend  
- Your friend runs it and gets an error âŒ  

Why?  
Because:
- Different Python version  
- Missing libraries  
